This plugin is an independent reimplementation of the ProtonDB-badge
injection concept popularised by the protondb-decky Decky-Loader plugin:

  https://github.com/OMGDuke/protondb-decky
  Dual-licensed: GPL-3.0 OR BSD-3-Clause
  Original Copyright (c) Steam Deck Homebrew

The upstream is dual-licensed; this plugin elects the BSD-3-Clause arm.
No source code from protondb-decky was copied or transliterated. Our
backend uses Chrome DevTools Protocol injection (the same architectural
pattern as our css-loader plugin), distinct from the Decky-frontend-lib
patching the upstream uses.

ProtonDB itself (https://www.protondb.com) is a third-party service and
is not affiliated with this project. We consume its public report-summary
API.
